text.__SUMMARY__: Conus scottjordani is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Conidae.
text.Original description: (of Cylindrus scottjordani Poppe, Monnier & Tagaro, 2012) Poppe G.T., Monnier E. & Tagaro S.P. (2012) New Conidae from the central Philippines. Visaya 3(5): 47-56. [March 2012]page(s): 47.
